      "span_text": "Cryostat sections of ovary tissue were stained with anti-mouse CD31 monoclonal antibody (BectonDickinson, Sunnyvale, CA, USA) with the aid of a HISTOFINE system (Nichirei Co., Tokyo, Japan) as described previously [CITATION_1] ."
